WEBVTT

00:00:00.880 --> 00:00:03.669
Good morning family, praise the Lord. I

00:00:03.679 --> 00:00:06.150
wanted to show you what the Lord did, and

00:00:06.160 --> 00:00:08.230
I believe this is a sign and a

00:00:08.240 --> 00:00:10.990
wonder for where

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:13.709
we were. Look, I put dye in there and

00:00:13.719 --> 00:00:17.349
it dyed my hand blue.

00:00:17.359 --> 00:00:18.950
I just want to give God praise

00:00:18.960 --> 00:00:21.830
because of what He did. We were in

00:00:21.840 --> 00:00:24.990
severe drought here in Oklahoma—a bad

00:00:24.990 --> 00:00:25.000
drought—and

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:27.070
it was

00:00:27.080 --> 00:00:29.630
starting to mount up to the point where there

00:00:29.630 --> 00:00:29.640
were

00:00:29.640 --> 00:00:31.509
fires and all kinds of stuff

00:00:31.519 --> 00:00:33.709
starting to happen going into the

00:00:33.719 --> 00:00:37.229
winter months.

00:00:37.239 --> 00:00:38.990
We don't get a lot of rain in the

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:41.229
winter, and we don't get a lot of

00:00:41.239 --> 00:00:43.510
rain at this time of the year in

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:47.069
November. But I set

00:00:47.079 --> 00:00:51.029
out and started praying over the weather

00:00:51.039 --> 00:00:53.549
back in October, speaking to the rain

00:00:53.549 --> 00:00:53.559
and

00:00:53.559 --> 00:00:55.910
calling it in. The Lord gave us an

00:00:55.920 --> 00:00:59.150
inch in 24 hours, and it's still

00:00:59.160 --> 00:01:00.950
going to rain all night

00:01:00.960 --> 00:01:03.630
tonight and all day tomorrow,

00:01:03.640 --> 00:01:07.630
which is amazing. In a 24-hour period,

00:01:07.640 --> 00:01:09.789
it filled up this gauge—five inches

00:01:09.789 --> 00:01:09.799
of rain—plus

00:01:09.799 --> 00:01:13.350
we got over an inch

00:01:13.360 --> 00:01:17.670
and a half, so six and a half inches of

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:23.149
rain in less than 48 hours so far.

00:01:23.159 --> 00:01:24.510
We have more

00:01:24.520 --> 00:01:27.230
coming. God is

00:01:27.240 --> 00:01:29.310
exceedingly abundantly above all that we

00:01:29.320 --> 00:01:31.350
dare ask or think. That's the kind of

00:01:31.360 --> 00:01:34.310
God we serve. If you just believe, all

00:01:34.320 --> 00:01:35.710
you have to do is stretch out there

00:01:35.720 --> 00:01:38.109
and believe by faith that you receive,

00:01:38.119 --> 00:01:39.749
calling those things that be not as

00:01:39.759 --> 00:01:41.630
though they were, speaking to the

00:01:41.640 --> 00:01:44.789
circumstances to change. Look, this is

00:01:44.799 --> 00:01:48.190
fruit. This is cold rain; I

00:01:48.190 --> 00:01:48.200
can

00:01:48.200 --> 00:01:50.069
feel it, it's making my fingers

00:01:50.079 --> 00:01:53.469
numb. I just wanted to say

00:01:53.479 --> 00:01:55.910
all things are possible to him

00:01:55.920 --> 00:01:57.550
that believes. Don't give up on what

00:01:57.560 --> 00:01:58.870
you're believing for. This is just

00:01:58.880 --> 00:02:01.109
something simple, but to the farmers, this

00:02:01.119 --> 00:02:03.870
is a big deal. Five inches of rain fills

00:02:03.880 --> 00:02:05.990
up the ponds and the lakes and gets

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:07.749
us through. We were going through

00:02:07.749 --> 00:02:07.759
a

00:02:07.759 --> 00:02:10.469
severe drought here in Oklahoma, but God

00:02:10.479 --> 00:02:12.710
can turn it around on

00:02:12.720 --> 00:02:15.350
a dime. If you just believe Him for

00:02:15.360 --> 00:02:18.110
the supernatural, believe Him for

00:02:18.120 --> 00:02:19.910
over and above all that you dare ask or

00:02:19.920 --> 00:02:21.990
think. We have more

00:02:21.990 --> 00:02:22.000
coming—six

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:25.070
and a half

00:02:25.070 --> 00:02:25.080
inches,

00:02:25.080 --> 00:02:28.509
folks, that's a lot of

00:02:28.519 --> 00:02:32.589
rain in 48 hours. Look at what Jesus

00:02:32.599 --> 00:02:35.270
does; it's like it parked over us and

00:02:35.280 --> 00:02:37.270
was

00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:40.390
dumping. Glory to God. We

00:02:40.400 --> 00:02:42.470
just want to tell you all thank you for

00:02:42.480 --> 00:02:44.710
joining us. My wife is going to

00:02:44.720 --> 00:02:47.910
come on today and talk to you all; she has

00:02:47.920 --> 00:02:50.869
a word from the Lord. The Lord woke her

00:02:50.879 --> 00:02:53.869
up and she has been sitting on this

00:02:53.879 --> 00:02:56.470
for a little bit because she prays over

00:02:56.480 --> 00:02:59.390
it like me. But I told her

00:02:59.400 --> 00:03:00.869
it's time for her to

00:03:00.879 --> 00:03:03.390
share that word the Lord gave

00:03:03.390 --> 00:03:03.400
her.

00:03:03.400 --> 00:03:05.670
She's going to talk to you all

00:03:05.680 --> 00:03:08.589
now about this word;

00:03:08.599 --> 00:03:11.030
she has two

00:03:11.040 --> 00:03:13.470
amazing words. She'll talk today

00:03:13.480 --> 00:03:15.470
and tomorrow

00:03:15.470 --> 00:03:15.480
about

00:03:15.480 --> 00:03:16.670
the things the Lord has been

00:03:16.680 --> 00:03:19.229
revealing to her. We'll pray

00:03:19.239 --> 00:03:21.070
together, take communion,

00:03:21.080 --> 00:03:22.390
and

00:03:22.400 --> 00:03:24.149
believe God. The

00:03:24.159 --> 00:03:25.630
Lord said He wants us to start praying

00:03:25.640 --> 00:03:27.550
more, so we're going to pray

00:03:27.550 --> 00:03:27.560
for

00:03:27.560 --> 00:03:30.830
no

00:03:30.840 --> 00:03:32.949
rioting because I've seen some riots

00:03:32.959 --> 00:03:34.949
in the spirit. The Lord told me to

00:03:34.959 --> 00:03:36.670
come against this rioting about the

00:03:36.680 --> 00:03:39.470
election results,

00:03:39.480 --> 00:03:41.550
against the spirit of

00:03:41.560 --> 00:03:44.309
division and the spirit of

00:03:44.319 --> 00:03:46.670
Antichrist, that our nation will not

00:03:46.680 --> 00:03:49.470
fall toward rioting and

00:03:49.480 --> 00:03:53.110
pillaging and people will

00:03:53.120 --> 00:03:56.350
cool their jets and be at peace. I

00:03:56.360 --> 00:03:58.910
believe this is a sign that

00:03:58.920 --> 00:04:01.670
it's time for the rain

00:04:01.680 --> 00:04:04.149
of the Holy Spirit and

00:04:04.159 --> 00:04:06.550
a supernatural drink. I hope you're

00:04:06.560 --> 00:04:08.550
thirsty today because Jesus is ready to

00:04:08.560 --> 00:04:11.350
fill you. Glory to God.

00:04:11.360 --> 00:04:13.149
Let's go straight to my wife now. 'Good

00:04:13.159 --> 00:04:15.910
morning family. I just wanted to come

00:04:15.920 --> 00:04:18.229
on and tell you this word the

00:04:18.239 --> 00:04:21.509
Lord spoke to me. It was in between my

00:04:21.519 --> 00:04:24.510
sleep and awake as I was waking up. He

00:04:24.520 --> 00:04:27.510
started speaking to me, and as I wrote,

00:04:27.520 --> 00:04:30.029
He paused until I

00:04:30.039 --> 00:04:31.550
could finish writing it down. It was

00:04:31.560 --> 00:04:32.430
just

00:04:32.440 --> 00:04:35.670
flowing; it

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:37.670
blessed me and I know it will bless

00:04:37.670 --> 00:04:37.680
you.

00:04:37.680 --> 00:04:41.070
He was

00:04:41.080 --> 00:04:42.029
showing

00:04:42.039 --> 00:04:45.350
me the ones

00:04:45.350 --> 00:04:45.360
He

00:04:45.360 --> 00:04:48.029
can trust more, He gives multiple

00:04:48.039 --> 00:04:50.670
endowments and can use them more. Then

00:04:50.680 --> 00:04:53.950
I saw a three-stranded cord: healing,

00:04:53.960 --> 00:04:57.830
glory, and prayer. Prayer must be a pillar, for

00:04:57.840 --> 00:05:00.310
it will sustain you.

00:05:00.320 --> 00:05:02.590
If you don't operate in a prayer gifting,

00:05:02.600 --> 00:05:04.150
who are you

00:05:04.150 --> 00:05:04.160
anyway?'The

00:05:04.160 --> 00:05:06.469
deeper you

00:05:06.479 --> 00:05:09.150
go with Me, the more I can use you. (I

00:05:09.160 --> 00:05:10.749
really like what you just said, I think

00:05:10.759 --> 00:05:12.749
you should emphasize that.) This

00:05:12.759 --> 00:05:15.830
is for every minister;

00:05:15.840 --> 00:05:17.909
this is for anybody who's called to the

00:05:17.919 --> 00:05:20.430
five-fold ministry to walk in the

00:05:20.440 --> 00:05:21.909
giftings He's called them to.

00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:27.670
What He's saying

00:05:27.670 --> 00:05:27.680
is

00:05:27.680 --> 00:05:30.909
the ones

00:05:30.909 --> 00:05:30.919
He

00:05:30.919 --> 00:05:34.150
can trust more, He gives multiple

00:05:34.160 --> 00:05:37.230
endowments and can use them more.

00:05:37.240 --> 00:05:39.749
I saw in the spirit a

00:05:39.749 --> 00:05:39.759
three-stranded

00:05:39.759 --> 00:05:42.189
cord intertwined like

00:05:42.199 --> 00:05:44.270
a rope, and

00:05:44.270 --> 00:05:44.280
the three-stranded

00:05:44.280 --> 00:05:47.670
cord was healing, glory, and prayer.

00:05:47.680 --> 00:05:49.710
He said prayer must be a pillar, for

00:05:49.720 --> 00:05:52.390
it will sustain you. If you don't

00:05:52.400 --> 00:05:54.230
operate in a prayer

00:05:54.240 --> 00:05:56.990
gifting, then who are you anyway?

00:05:57.000 --> 00:05:59.790
Prayer is your foundation.

00:05:59.800 --> 00:06:01.110
As

00:06:07.309 --> 00:06:07.319
He

00:06:10.039 --> 00:06:12.870
was

00:06:18.639 --> 00:06:20.870
speaking to me, I'm just

00:06:20.880 --> 00:06:23.990
trembling and shaking. I saw in

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:25.950
the spirit that I was before His throne

00:06:25.960 --> 00:06:27.710
room.

00:06:30.560 --> 00:06:33.390
I felt

00:06:33.400 --> 00:06:36.510
His tangible presence fall on me. Then

00:06:36.520 --> 00:06:38.909
He said, 'The deeper you go with Me, the

00:06:38.919 --> 00:06:41.870
more I can use you, and the more I will

00:06:41.880 --> 00:06:45.350
require of

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:49.350
you. For if you truly know My heart, you

00:06:49.360 --> 00:06:52.309
know if I can't move through you and get

00:06:52.319 --> 00:06:55.070
it out to others, then what use

00:06:55.080 --> 00:06:58.510
are you?'If you're asking

00:06:58.520 --> 00:07:01.189
for the Lord to use you and He

00:07:01.199 --> 00:07:03.070
puts an anointing on you,

00:07:03.070 --> 00:07:03.080
but

00:07:03.080 --> 00:07:04.710
He can't get it through you because

00:07:04.720 --> 00:07:07.869
you're in fear or

00:07:07.869 --> 00:07:07.879
unwilling

00:07:07.879 --> 00:07:10.230
to

00:07:10.240 --> 00:07:13.150
talk to that individual, then

00:07:13.160 --> 00:07:14.670
what use are you to Him? You're

00:07:14.680 --> 00:07:17.029
bottling it up.

00:07:17.039 --> 00:07:19.990
Check your heart each and every

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:22.710
day; this is vital for you in the coming

00:07:22.720 --> 00:07:25.749
days and

00:07:25.759 --> 00:07:28.589
always.

00:07:28.599 --> 00:07:31.070
It's for your

00:07:31.080 --> 00:07:34.710
protection. He will not be mocked; He will

00:07:34.720 --> 00:07:38.710
have a move and manifestation of

00:07:38.710 --> 00:07:38.720
His

00:07:38.720 --> 00:07:41.589
glory. Then He was talking

00:07:41.599 --> 00:07:44.589
about what the Lord told Brandon about

00:07:44.599 --> 00:07:46.710
the older generation going

00:07:46.710 --> 00:07:46.720
home—the

00:07:46.720 --> 00:07:49.230
greats. There's going to be a

00:07:49.240 --> 00:07:52.270
great

00:07:52.270 --> 00:07:52.280
baton

00:07:52.280 --> 00:07:56.070
passing. He said they have asked,

00:07:56.070 --> 00:07:56.080
but

00:07:56.080 --> 00:07:58.230
in their heart, they are

00:07:58.240 --> 00:08:00.950
tired. They use it as an excuse, and I'm

00:08:00.960 --> 00:08:03.510
tired of hearing it.

00:08:03.520 --> 00:08:06.469
If I

00:08:06.479 --> 00:08:09.710
can't move through you, I have no use of

00:08:09.720 --> 00:08:12.350
you. They've had long

00:08:12.360 --> 00:08:15.550
lives; this is a promotion.

00:08:15.560 --> 00:08:18.510
They

00:08:18.520 --> 00:08:20.270
are

00:08:20.280 --> 00:08:21.589
coming

00:08:21.599 --> 00:08:24.749
home. But they have begged Me

00:08:24.759 --> 00:08:27.390
to use them mightily, and they cannot ask

00:08:27.400 --> 00:08:29.070
the things they have asked then turn

00:08:29.080 --> 00:08:31.990
their back on Me. It's a stench to My

00:08:32.000 --> 00:08:34.670
nose.

00:08:34.680 --> 00:08:38.149
You can't ask Me to use you and ask

00:08:38.159 --> 00:08:40.750
for long life then withhold yourself

00:08:40.760 --> 00:08:43.509
from allowing Me to distribute the

00:08:43.519 --> 00:08:48.190
impartations. My gifts will not be held

00:08:48.200 --> 00:08:50.550
hostage. They either move

00:08:50.560 --> 00:08:52.790
with Me or I'm calling them home. They

00:08:52.800 --> 00:08:56.389
say, 'Why, Lord? Why

00:08:56.399 --> 00:08:58.790
do you want me to do that?'and I'm

00:08:58.800 --> 00:08:59.949
tired of it.

00:08:59.959 --> 00:09:02.630
Get in sync with Me or get off the boat.

00:09:02.640 --> 00:09:06.150
I'm not held back by age, race, or time. This

00:09:06.160 --> 00:09:08.750
is a mockery of My

00:09:08.760 --> 00:09:10.750
endowment.

00:09:10.760 --> 00:09:12.350
Think about what He just

00:09:12.360 --> 00:09:15.750
said. He's not moved by age,

00:09:15.750 --> 00:09:15.760
skin

00:09:15.760 --> 00:09:19.590
color, or time. If

00:09:19.600 --> 00:09:21.670
you say He can't use you because of

00:09:21.670 --> 00:09:21.680
your

00:09:21.680 --> 00:09:25.110
race, you're missing it.

00:09:30.640 --> 00:09:33.470
Man looks at dumb

00:09:33.480 --> 00:09:36.829
stuff, but God looks at the heart.

00:09:38.519 --> 00:09:41.350
Get in sync with Me or

00:09:41.360 --> 00:09:43.470
get off the boat.

00:09:55.959 --> 00:09:58.710
He'll use whoever will yield himself to

00:09:58.720 --> 00:10:02.550
Him. 'Be

00:10:02.560 --> 00:10:05.150
careful what you ask for if you cannot

00:10:05.160 --> 00:10:07.350
be in sync with Me and check your pride

00:10:07.360 --> 00:10:09.430
at the door. If you question Me all along

00:10:09.440 --> 00:10:12.829
the way, then you shouldn't be asking for

00:10:12.839 --> 00:10:16.870
it. There's no time; I don't have time to

00:10:16.880 --> 00:10:19.509
keep explaining myself to My

00:10:19.509 --> 00:10:19.519
refiners.'I

00:10:19.519 --> 00:10:22.910
love that He referred to

00:10:22.910 --> 00:10:22.920
them

00:10:22.920 --> 00:10:27.590
as

00:10:27.590 --> 00:10:27.600
refiners—the

00:10:27.600 --> 00:10:28.710
ones who have been through

00:10:28.720 --> 00:10:30.470
that refining fire.

00:10:30.480 --> 00:10:33.990
'If I can't move through

00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:36.910
you, I have no more use

00:10:36.920 --> 00:10:40.069
of you. So be careful, daughter, what you

00:10:40.079 --> 00:10:42.470
ask for, because everything I

00:10:42.480 --> 00:10:45.310
endow I will place a demand on, not just

00:10:45.320 --> 00:10:47.949
for a measure of time. There's a greater

00:10:47.959 --> 00:10:50.590
purpose for My movement and

00:10:50.590 --> 00:10:50.600
the

00:10:50.600 --> 00:10:53.670
manifestation of My glory. The harvest is

00:10:53.680 --> 00:10:56.150
plenty and the laborers are few.

00:10:56.160 --> 00:10:59.550
Many

00:10:59.560 --> 00:11:02.110
have asked, I have given, and they

00:11:02.120 --> 00:11:04.870
withhold. This will not

00:11:04.880 --> 00:11:08.629
happen. Be quick to obey. Stay

00:11:08.639 --> 00:11:12.030
in sync with Me, do a heart check every day,

00:11:12.040 --> 00:11:14.910
and you'll be okay.

00:11:14.920 --> 00:11:18.389
Do not ask for it

00:11:18.399 --> 00:11:20.550
and then complain when I ask you to use

00:11:20.560 --> 00:11:23.550
it for a greater purpose. Why

00:11:23.560 --> 00:11:25.629
would I give a gift endowment and not

00:11:25.639 --> 00:11:28.870
use it mightily? What use is a tool if it

00:11:28.880 --> 00:11:31.629
runs away and hides itself from Me? Do

00:11:31.639 --> 00:11:33.910
not ask things of Me and then run from

00:11:33.920 --> 00:11:37.509
Me as Adam and Eve did. With long life I

00:11:37.519 --> 00:11:39.910
will satisfy you, they keep saying,

00:11:42.079 --> 00:11:45.389
but they aren't satisfying Me. I

00:11:45.399 --> 00:11:47.790
will not be

00:11:47.790 --> 00:11:47.800
mocked.'They

00:11:47.800 --> 00:11:50.590
are

00:11:50.600 --> 00:11:52.030
using that

00:11:52.040 --> 00:11:54.150
scripture against Him, saying, 'Lord, you

00:11:54.160 --> 00:11:55.910
said with long life You'll satisfy

00:11:58.230 --> 00:11:58.240
me,'but

00:12:00.839 --> 00:12:03.150
they're not satisfying the Lord.

00:12:08.399 --> 00:12:10.230
He's trying to do something through them

00:12:10.240 --> 00:12:13.829
to save humanity for these last days, and

00:12:13.839 --> 00:12:16.870
they are like a stone wall to Him.

00:12:16.880 --> 00:12:18.150
'You're quoting these

00:12:18.160 --> 00:12:19.550
scriptures at Me, but you're not

00:12:19.560 --> 00:12:22.430
satisfying Me.

00:12:28.920 --> 00:12:31.790
Do not

00:12:31.800 --> 00:12:33.829
ask for it and then complain when I ask

00:12:33.839 --> 00:12:36.710
you to use it.

00:12:38.920 --> 00:12:41.629
What

00:12:41.639 --> 00:12:44.189
use is a tool if it runs away and hides

00:12:44.199 --> 00:12:46.910
itself from Me? Do not ask things of Me

00:12:46.920 --> 00:12:50.430
and then run like Adam and Eve did.

00:12:50.440 --> 00:12:53.310
With long life I will satisfy you,

00:12:53.320 --> 00:12:55.069
they keep saying, but they aren't

00:12:55.079 --> 00:12:58.629
satisfying Me. I will not be mocked.

00:12:58.639 --> 00:13:00.949
Instead of asking for My help for

00:13:00.959 --> 00:13:03.470
healing, energy, or youth renewed

00:13:03.480 --> 00:13:05.629
like an eagle, they withhold themselves

00:13:05.639 --> 00:13:08.710
from Me. I'm tired, Lord, they say. Well,

00:13:08.720 --> 00:13:10.230
come home

00:13:10.230 --> 00:13:10.240
then.'Then

00:13:10.240 --> 00:13:14.030
I saw a marriage bed where

00:13:14.030 --> 00:13:14.040
a

00:13:14.040 --> 00:13:16.509
wife would say she's too tired.

00:13:16.519 --> 00:13:19.790
The deeper

00:13:19.800 --> 00:13:22.189
you go with Me, be careful and don't get

00:13:22.199 --> 00:13:25.030
burned.

00:13:29.560 --> 00:13:32.310
If you abide in Me

00:13:32.320 --> 00:13:34.269
and My words abide in you, ask what you

00:13:34.279 --> 00:13:36.470
will and it will be done for you.

00:13:36.480 --> 00:13:39.310
I was asking Him to pluck anything

00:13:39.320 --> 00:13:41.150
up in my heart that's bad and fix

00:13:41.160 --> 00:13:42.550
me, and He said, 'I know, daughter, you're

00:13:42.560 --> 00:13:46.189
good. I'm just telling you what I require

00:13:46.199 --> 00:13:47.870
of you so you know what you're

00:13:47.880 --> 00:13:51.030
getting into. I am not a fine-print

00:13:51.030 --> 00:13:51.040
God.'Think

00:13:51.040 --> 00:13:52.790
about

00:13:52.800 --> 00:13:55.350
that.

00:13:55.360 --> 00:13:58.470
He

00:13:58.480 --> 00:14:01.310
is

00:14:01.320 --> 00:14:03.550
bold; you

00:14:03.550 --> 00:14:03.560
don't

00:14:03.560 --> 00:14:04.910
have to guess what God's

00:14:04.920 --> 00:14:07.590
trying to tell you to do. You don't have to

00:14:07.600 --> 00:14:10.110
read fine print

00:14:10.120 --> 00:14:13.189
like you see on

00:14:13.199 --> 00:14:14.829
those cartoons

00:14:14.839 --> 00:14:17.949
or

00:14:20.389 --> 00:14:20.399
in

00:14:22.120 --> 00:14:23.949
the

00:14:25.590 --> 00:14:25.600
movies.

00:14:27.430 --> 00:14:27.440
God's

00:14:29.240 --> 00:14:30.710
word

00:14:33.110 --> 00:14:33.120
is

00:14:36.279 --> 00:14:38.350
bold, black and white.

00:14:40.240 --> 00:14:41.829
He said,

00:14:41.839 --> 00:14:45.189
'I am not a

00:14:50.749 --> 00:14:50.759
fine-print

00:14:57.759 --> 00:15:00.749
God. I am El Shaddai,

00:15:00.749 --> 00:15:00.759
the all-consuming

00:15:00.759 --> 00:15:03.949
fire. The revival can't

00:15:03.959 --> 00:15:06.430
happen until my harvesters are

00:15:14.030 --> 00:15:14.040
ready.'He

00:15:20.240 --> 00:15:23.030
has to have us to bring in the

00:15:23.040 --> 00:15:24.949
harvest. He can't bring in the

00:15:24.959 --> 00:15:27.389
revival until His

00:15:27.399 --> 00:15:29.269
harvesters are ready. Are you getting

00:15:29.279 --> 00:15:31.790
ready? Are you

00:15:34.360 --> 00:15:38.230
sold out?

00:15:40.639 --> 00:15:43.629
'The revival cannot happen until

00:15:43.639 --> 00:15:46.790
My harvest is ready. Don't make excuses

00:15:46.800 --> 00:15:49.670
to Me. Ask Me to make a way for you if

00:15:49.680 --> 00:15:52.269
you need something. Don't

00:15:52.279 --> 00:15:54.829
ever come before Me and make excuses.

00:15:54.839 --> 00:15:58.430
I will not be mocked. If you don't ask,

00:15:58.440 --> 00:16:01.069
I can't give it to you. I'm not a

00:16:01.069 --> 00:16:01.079
fine-print

00:16:01.079 --> 00:16:04.509
God; I want to bless you. This isn't

00:16:04.519 --> 00:16:07.509
a trap. I love you, and I'm not looking to

00:16:07.509 --> 00:16:07.519
ensnare

00:16:07.519 --> 00:16:09.629
you. I'm not like your earthly

00:16:09.639 --> 00:16:12.749
father. My yes is yes, and My no is no.

00:16:12.759 --> 00:16:15.069
There's no gray

00:16:15.079 --> 00:16:17.710
with Me. Come before My

00:16:17.720 --> 00:16:20.389
throne boldly with grace. No good thing

00:16:20.399 --> 00:16:23.990
will He withhold from them who walk

00:16:23.990 --> 00:16:24.000
uprightly.'I

00:16:24.000 --> 00:16:26.629
forgot to tell

00:16:26.639 --> 00:16:28.670
you that at the beginning of this, I

00:16:28.680 --> 00:16:30.749
had a 4% battery

00:16:30.749 --> 00:16:30.759
and

00:16:30.759 --> 00:16:34.269
couldn't find a charger.

00:16:34.279 --> 00:16:37.550
I said, 'Lord, preserve my battery so I can

00:16:37.560 --> 00:16:39.629
write everything you're telling

00:16:39.629 --> 00:16:39.639
me.'He

00:16:39.639 --> 00:16:41.790
laughed and said, 'You come

00:16:41.800 --> 00:16:43.870
before My throne with such a small

00:16:43.880 --> 00:16:46.590
request,

00:16:46.590 --> 00:16:46.600
daughter.'I

00:16:46.600 --> 00:16:48.309
kept

00:16:48.319 --> 00:16:51.269
writing

00:16:51.279 --> 00:16:52.910
for

00:16:52.920 --> 00:16:55.030
over two hours,

00:16:55.040 --> 00:16:57.670
and

00:16:57.680 --> 00:17:01.230
when He finished

00:17:01.240 --> 00:17:04.549
talking, it was at 1%. God is amazing.

00:17:11.640 --> 00:17:13.909
He said, 'If you sync up with Me,

00:17:13.919 --> 00:17:15.870
you won't have to ask what the now

00:17:15.880 --> 00:17:17.990
word is. If you're asking,

00:17:18.000 --> 00:17:20.470
you've been out of sync for a while.

00:17:24.039 --> 00:17:27.990
I'm not a mean God; I'm focused. I

00:17:28.000 --> 00:17:30.150
know exactly what needs to happen, and

00:17:30.160 --> 00:17:32.590
I'm tired of having to explain myself.

00:17:32.600 --> 00:17:36.750
Get in sync or come home to

00:17:36.750 --> 00:17:36.760
Me.'I

00:17:36.760 --> 00:17:40.029
was thinking

00:17:40.039 --> 00:17:41.830
that

00:17:41.840 --> 00:17:43.029
sounded

00:17:43.039 --> 00:17:45.110
harsh, and He said, 'It's not

00:17:45.120 --> 00:17:47.710
harsh. They knew what I require of them,

00:17:47.720 --> 00:17:50.310
yet they offer excuses.

00:17:50.320 --> 00:17:53.470
I will not be

00:17:53.470 --> 00:17:53.480
mocked.'I

00:17:53.480 --> 00:17:55.789
asked why He was telling me all this,

00:17:55.799 --> 00:17:57.430
and He said, 'You asked what was on My

00:17:57.440 --> 00:17:59.750
heart

00:17:59.760 --> 00:18:01.590
today.'He

00:18:01.600 --> 00:18:03.669
said no one's perfect, but

00:18:03.669 --> 00:18:03.679
He's

00:18:03.679 --> 00:18:05.390
asking

00:18:05.390 --> 00:18:05.400
us

00:18:05.400 --> 00:18:08.669
to stay usable. 'Don't

00:18:15.720 --> 00:18:17.549
come before My throne

00:18:17.559 --> 00:18:20.190
with excuses; I'm fed up with them. They

00:18:22.320 --> 00:18:24.950
tell

00:18:24.960 --> 00:18:27.630
Me what they aren't going to do and why;

00:18:27.640 --> 00:18:30.270
it's a stench.

00:18:32.840 --> 00:18:35.830
I am not a genie in a

00:18:37.760 --> 00:18:40.110
bottle.'Then

00:18:43.240 --> 00:18:45.990
He started

00:18:46.000 --> 00:18:48.350
talking about finances. He said if He can

00:18:48.360 --> 00:18:51.270
trust you, He will give more to you.

00:18:54.480 --> 00:18:56.950
If

00:18:56.950 --> 00:18:56.960
people

00:18:56.960 --> 00:18:59.230
withhold finances,

00:18:59.230 --> 00:18:59.240
it

00:18:59.240 --> 00:19:00.870
means they love money more

00:19:00.880 --> 00:19:03.430
than

00:19:03.440 --> 00:19:06.430
Him.

00:19:06.440 --> 00:19:08.909
He said, 'You passed the test

00:19:08.919 --> 00:19:11.470
with finances; I'm

00:19:11.480 --> 00:19:13.270
pleased.'I

00:19:15.669 --> 00:19:15.679
asked

00:19:18.360 --> 00:19:20.110
what I

00:19:20.110 --> 00:19:20.120
could

00:19:20.120 --> 00:19:21.909
do for

00:19:21.909 --> 00:19:21.919
Him,

00:19:21.919 --> 00:19:25.669
and He said, 'Stay in sync; don't

00:19:25.679 --> 00:19:28.270
become like them.'I asked

00:19:28.270 --> 00:19:28.280
if I could

00:19:28.280 --> 00:19:30.350
pray for them, and He said,

00:19:30.360 --> 00:19:33.430
'Prayer is a sweet sound,

00:19:33.440 --> 00:19:35.669
but prayer won't change this. Their

00:19:35.679 --> 00:19:37.630
hearts are hardened in this

00:19:37.630 --> 00:19:37.640
area.'He's

00:19:37.640 --> 00:19:39.669
talking about

00:19:39.679 --> 00:19:42.029
ministers who have

00:19:42.039 --> 00:19:44.110
become callous

00:19:44.110 --> 00:19:44.120
and

00:19:44.120 --> 00:19:46.070
puffed up

00:19:51.159 --> 00:19:53.310
because of

00:20:14.919 --> 00:20:17.070
their

00:20:31.120 --> 00:20:33.070
platforms.

00:20:47.799 --> 00:20:50.549
They feel they are equal with Him or

00:20:50.559 --> 00:20:53.029
bigger than Him. They stop checking in because they think they already

00:20:53.039 --> 00:20:55.230
know what He's going to say.

00:20:55.240 --> 00:20:58.430
They put Him in a box

00:20:58.430 --> 00:20:58.440
and

00:20:58.440 --> 00:21:01.149
get out of

00:21:14.310 --> 00:21:14.320
sync.

00:21:28.000 --> 00:21:30.350
Don't

00:21:30.360 --> 00:21:33.149
become reliant on the gift; stay reliant

00:21:33.159 --> 00:21:35.190
on Me.

00:21:35.200 --> 00:21:37.830
When you

00:21:37.840 --> 00:21:39.350
start flowing in the Holy Spirit

00:21:39.350 --> 00:21:39.360
and

00:21:39.360 --> 00:21:40.950
seeing signs

00:21:40.960 --> 00:21:43.750
and wonders, don't

00:21:43.750 --> 00:21:43.760
stop spending

00:21:43.760 --> 00:21:46.510
time with Him every day.

00:22:18.559 --> 00:22:21.870
Without Him, who are we? Without

00:22:21.880 --> 00:22:24.070
prayer, who are you

00:22:24.080 --> 00:22:27.350
anyway? It must be a pillar. You

00:22:29.679 --> 00:22:33.510
must fear God more

00:22:33.520 --> 00:22:36.390
than man. Follow

00:22:36.390 --> 00:22:36.400
His

00:22:36.400 --> 00:22:38.149
leadings and promptings, and

00:22:38.149 --> 00:22:38.159
He's

00:22:38.159 --> 00:22:40.630
got your back. You

00:22:42.799 --> 00:22:46.390
work for Him; fear

00:22:46.390 --> 00:22:46.400
Him.

00:22:46.400 --> 00:22:48.230
I feel

00:23:04.080 --> 00:23:06.070
the bottom line

00:23:06.080 --> 00:23:08.070
is

00:23:08.080 --> 00:23:11.789
for the body of Christ to know that

00:23:11.799 --> 00:23:14.430
He's out of

00:23:14.440 --> 00:23:16.870
time. Jesus Christ

00:23:16.880 --> 00:23:17.669
is

00:23:17.679 --> 00:23:20.510
coming, and without His

00:23:20.520 --> 00:23:23.909
people yielding

00:23:23.909 --> 00:23:23.919
themselves,

00:23:23.919 --> 00:23:26.630
He

00:23:26.630 --> 00:23:26.640
cannot

00:23:26.640 --> 00:23:28.630
flow through them.

00:23:28.630 --> 00:23:28.640
It must

00:23:28.640 --> 00:23:33.110
be frustrating

00:23:33.110 --> 00:23:33.120
for

00:23:33.120 --> 00:23:36.470
God; He wants to

00:23:36.470 --> 00:23:36.480
get things done

00:23:36.480 --> 00:23:38.669
on

00:23:42.840 --> 00:23:44.950
Earth,

00:23:51.880 --> 00:23:53.350
but He deals with

00:23:53.360 --> 00:23:56.830
knuckleheads who say they're tired.

00:23:56.840 --> 00:23:59.029
He

00:24:00.830 --> 00:24:00.840
could

00:24:03.870 --> 00:24:03.880
appear

00:24:07.120 --> 00:24:10.269
as Elohim or Jehovah Jireh

00:24:10.269 --> 00:24:10.279
and say,

00:24:10.279 --> 00:24:13.230
'I am God, get

00:24:13.230 --> 00:24:13.240
saved,'but

00:24:13.240 --> 00:24:16.430
He uses us.

00:24:19.440 --> 00:24:22.190
How bad do you

00:24:22.200 --> 00:24:26.590
want it?

00:24:29.120 --> 00:24:32.669
Do you want change or not?

00:24:38.120 --> 00:24:40.750
If

00:24:40.760 --> 00:24:42.710
He gives you a gift, are you going to hold it

00:24:42.710 --> 00:24:42.720
hostage or

00:24:42.720 --> 00:24:44.830
let Him use it

00:24:52.039 --> 00:24:54.990
for

00:24:55.000 --> 00:24:57.669
the greater purpose?

00:24:57.669 --> 00:24:57.679
Don't

00:24:57.679 --> 00:24:59.750
get a big head

00:24:59.750 --> 00:24:59.760
and

00:24:59.760 --> 00:25:02.230
think for Him.

00:25:19.080 --> 00:25:20.430
That's why He was correcting me

00:25:20.440 --> 00:25:21.549
about the Yankees—I

00:25:21.549 --> 00:25:21.559
was

00:25:21.559 --> 00:25:23.830
trying to think for Him.

00:25:27.159 --> 00:25:30.710
Don't

00:25:35.080 --> 00:25:37.990
hide yourself

00:25:40.640 --> 00:25:43.510
because you're intimidated or

00:25:45.880 --> 00:25:47.549
care too much

00:25:47.559 --> 00:25:49.149
about

00:25:49.159 --> 00:25:52.190
people's

00:25:52.200 --> 00:25:54.630
opinions.

00:25:54.640 --> 00:25:57.110
Stay

00:25:57.120 --> 00:25:58.950
in

00:25:58.960 --> 00:26:01.669
sync

00:26:01.679 --> 00:26:03.029
like

00:26:03.039 --> 00:26:04.510
the

00:26:04.520 --> 00:26:05.909
ticking of a

00:26:05.919 --> 00:26:08.950
clock.

00:26:26.559 --> 00:26:28.710
He knows exactly what

00:26:28.720 --> 00:26:30.110
you're supposed to do

00:26:30.120 --> 00:26:32.510
daily

00:26:32.510 --> 00:26:32.520
and

00:26:32.520 --> 00:26:36.029
hourly.

00:26:45.200 --> 00:26:49.310
The

00:26:49.320 --> 00:26:52.350
Bible says to pray without ceasing.

00:27:04.760 --> 00:27:07.070
The

00:27:07.080 --> 00:27:09.750
disciples

00:27:09.760 --> 00:27:12.269
were filled

00:27:12.279 --> 00:27:14.909
with and controlled by the Holy Spirit

00:27:14.919 --> 00:27:16.590
because

00:27:16.600 --> 00:27:18.110
they

00:27:18.120 --> 00:27:20.310
sought

00:27:20.320 --> 00:27:23.389
Him hourly. Smith

00:27:23.399 --> 00:27:26.350
Wigglesworth was a

00:27:26.360 --> 00:27:27.950
great man of God

00:27:27.960 --> 00:27:30.310
who

00:27:34.520 --> 00:27:36.750
raised

00:27:36.750 --> 00:27:36.760
many

00:27:36.760 --> 00:27:38.190
from the dead.

00:27:40.549 --> 00:27:40.559
He

00:27:44.240 --> 00:27:47.110
carried

00:27:51.240 --> 00:27:53.389
an Old

00:27:53.389 --> 00:27:53.399
and

00:27:53.399 --> 00:27:55.710
New Testament in his

00:27:55.720 --> 00:27:58.190
pockets

00:27:58.190 --> 00:27:58.200
and

00:27:58.200 --> 00:28:00.669
would read

00:28:00.669 --> 00:28:00.679
them

00:28:00.679 --> 00:28:03.230
every 15 minutes

00:28:03.240 --> 00:28:05.269
to

00:28:05.279 --> 00:28:08.669
stay

00:28:08.679 --> 00:28:11.990
filled

00:28:12.000 --> 00:28:14.549
with the spirit.

00:28:22.440 --> 00:28:25.669
That's what

00:28:25.679 --> 00:28:27.430
it

00:28:27.440 --> 00:28:29.029
takes:

00:28:29.039 --> 00:28:32.269
being sold out.

00:28:42.760 --> 00:28:45.870
Have prayer as your foundation and

00:28:45.880 --> 00:28:47.950
don't give

00:28:47.960 --> 00:28:50.110
excuses.

00:28:52.000 --> 00:28:55.149
God is

00:28:55.149 --> 00:28:55.159
a

00:28:55.159 --> 00:28:58.669
bold God.

00:29:03.320 --> 00:29:06.470
We make things so

00:29:06.480 --> 00:29:09.149
religious,

00:29:09.159 --> 00:29:11.669
but

00:29:11.679 --> 00:29:13.909
even a child can

00:29:13.919 --> 00:29:16.430
follow Him.

00:29:16.440 --> 00:29:18.669
He's

00:29:18.679 --> 00:29:20.789
not looking to ensnare you.

00:29:38.000 --> 00:29:41.269
Can He use

00:29:41.279 --> 00:29:44.430
you like He did Billy Graham, Reinhard Bonnke, R.W. Schambach, Kenneth Hagin, or

00:29:53.080 --> 00:29:56.509
Jack

00:29:56.519 --> 00:30:00.830
Coe?

00:30:00.840 --> 00:30:02.710
It's one thing to ask

00:30:02.720 --> 00:30:06.389
to be used

00:30:06.389 --> 00:30:06.399
and

00:30:06.399 --> 00:30:07.990
another to submit

00:30:08.000 --> 00:30:11.750
yourself fully to

00:30:13.000 --> 00:30:16.070
the refiner's

00:30:23.679 --> 00:30:26.389
fire.

00:30:34.840 --> 00:30:37.470
I know beyond a

00:30:37.480 --> 00:30:39.950
shadow of a doubt that Jesus

00:30:39.960 --> 00:30:41.070
is

00:30:41.080 --> 00:30:43.750
coming, but He's

00:30:43.760 --> 00:30:45.789
not coming until

00:30:45.789 --> 00:30:45.799
He

00:30:45.799 --> 00:30:46.789
has

00:30:46.789 --> 00:30:46.799
His

00:30:46.799 --> 00:30:51.190
harvest.

00:30:51.200 --> 00:30:53.389
He's

00:30:53.399 --> 00:30:56.669
waiting

00:30:59.669 --> 00:30:59.679
for

00:31:02.669 --> 00:31:02.679
people

00:31:05.039 --> 00:31:07.430
like

00:31:15.840 --> 00:31:19.269
us

00:31:27.600 --> 00:31:29.710
to be the mouthpiece. Be quick to

00:31:29.710 --> 00:31:29.720
obey, whether

00:31:29.720 --> 00:31:33.350
it's

00:31:33.360 --> 00:31:34.909
witnessing

00:31:34.919 --> 00:31:36.549
in

00:31:36.559 --> 00:31:38.629
Walmart or helping someone

00:31:38.629 --> 00:31:38.639
with a tank

00:31:38.639 --> 00:31:42.909
of gas. You

00:31:42.909 --> 00:31:42.919
never know

00:31:42.919 --> 00:31:45.669
what

00:31:55.519 --> 00:31:59.430
someone

00:32:09.519 --> 00:32:11.669
is

00:32:21.360 --> 00:32:23.789
going

00:32:30.320 --> 00:32:33.509
through;

00:32:38.639 --> 00:32:41.149
they could be at their

00:32:41.159 --> 00:32:43.230
wit's end, and

00:32:43.230 --> 00:32:43.240
your

00:32:43.240 --> 00:32:46.190
obedience

00:32:46.190 --> 00:32:46.200
shows

00:32:46.200 --> 00:32:48.870
them the love of God.

00:32:52.590 --> 00:32:52.600
Diana

00:32:57.240 --> 00:33:00.190
bought

00:33:04.480 --> 00:33:06.549
tracts

00:33:11.789 --> 00:33:11.799
for

00:33:15.360 --> 00:33:18.070
us

00:33:21.519 --> 00:33:23.789
to keep

00:33:26.600 --> 00:33:29.310
in

00:33:34.070 --> 00:33:34.080
the

00:33:37.159 --> 00:33:39.269
car.

00:33:49.799 --> 00:33:52.830
When she was

00:33:54.799 --> 00:34:00.110
five,

00:34:00.110 --> 00:34:00.120
she

00:34:00.120 --> 00:34:03.549
found

